{"tid":678463,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"菲律賓主題公園出現劣質《海賊王》雕像  草帽團被黑出新高度","createTime":"2018-05-26T05:54:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-26T09:49:37.000Z","uid":49391,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"a457d0081ec5e470aa776cc7c444e47e3f83210f","tid":678463,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T05:54:05.000Z","msg":"近日，有網友在推特爆料並貼圖，表示菲律賓的一處山寨主題公園出現了《海賊王》裡草帽團的劣質雕像，路飛、娜美、索隆和山治等角色被黑了個遍。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img1.gamersky.com/image2018/05/20180526_sy_225_2/gamersky_01small_02_2018526955EA8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg1.gamersky.com%2Fimage2018%2F05%2F20180526_sy_225_2%2Fgamersky_01small_02_2018526955EA8.jpg&h=34deb18e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n這個被爆料的地方位於菲律賓布拉幹省的Jed's Island Resort，長年以擺放各種動漫角色的劣質雕像而聞名。據知情人透露，園方是考慮到所有角色均未取得授權，才把它們製作得如此古怪。在此之前，《高達》的RX-78、《火影忍者》的鳴人、《龍珠》的悟空，以及迪士尼的各種動漫角色紛紛躺槍，場面可謂&ldquo;美不勝收&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img1.gamersky.com/image2018/05/20180526_sy_225_2/gamersky_03small_06_201852695533D.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg1.gamersky.com%2Fimage2018%2F05%2F20180526_sy_225_2%2Fgamersky_03small_06_201852695533D.jpg&h=ce437ecd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img1.gamersky.com/image2018/05/20180526_sy_225_2/gamersky_04small_08_2018526955A2E.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg1.gamersky.com%2Fimage2018%2F05%2F20180526_sy_225_2%2Fgamersky_04small_08_2018526955A2E.jpg&h=99beea0d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n而在最近，園方又把毒手伸向了全球馳名的《海賊王》，打造出一系列草帽團雕像，依然魔性十足。光從外表來看，路飛那迷人的大眼、被毀容的娜美、如同吃了橡膠果實一樣的索隆、嘴巴歪斜的烏索普、被加裝神秘配件的喬巴都讓人無力吐槽，相比之下好像就山治顯得還算正常一點&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img1.gamersky.com/image2018/05/20180526_sy_225_2/gamersky_02small_04_2018526955481.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg1.gamersky.com%2Fimage2018%2F05%2F20180526_sy_225_2%2Fgamersky_02small_04_2018526955481.jpg&h=584a4e15&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"67d748a2476c625bfb3566d93dea892b692aca27","tid":678463,"uid":57835,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T06:03:28.000Z","msg":"因為唔想侵權？手工差咪認囉"},{"pid":"e0beaeca5a8e3c22b8986c3a95b04bff5a5763e9","tid":678463,"uid":45477,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T06:11:19.000Z","msg":"咁抽像<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1967e090374e49a4a1aeb7fabbf4acbc84b4dbe3","tid":678463,"uid":2566,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T06:15:44.000Z","msg":"屌你個娜美，雞頭咁款<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2523c467057eb0a9acd2bdf2e7443929920ae4f1","tid":678463,"uid":55568,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T06:16:51.000Z","msg":"大大個oneprice logo印住仲講版權"},{"pid":"f82d26fc3e0848072338aabbba3b8d119689062e","tid":678463,"uid":129521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T08:52:19.000Z","msg":"黑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d44f6e57c48211d3fcf6bf8b3d84b1b25c4a2d4b","tid":678463,"uid":70505,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"2523c467057eb0a9acd2bdf2e7443929920ae4f1","tid":678463,"uid":55568,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T06:16:51.000Z","msg":"大大個oneprice logo印住仲講版權"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T08:54:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c326d341abcc14083e112ac1aae701b223c3da68","tid":678463,"uid":55045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T09:12:51.000Z","msg":"娜美俾人打腫左半邊臉咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b024a79657de4bebbc3c91efc4e9b1b660a1acb","tid":678463,"uid":22913,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote"